verbose_text: When expressed at low levels, K-RBP synergizes with K-Rta transactivation of the Mta, K-bZIP, vIL-6, K-Rta, and vMIP-1 promoters, but at high levels, represses K-Rta transactivation of K-bZIP, Mta, and PAN promoters.
